  "title": "Bookkeeper (Full-Set) | Jurong East - YZ11",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Bookkeeper (Full set accounts)</strong></u></p><ul><li>Monday - Friday (9-6PM)</li><li>Address: Jurong East</li><li>Salary: $2000 - $2800 </li></ul><p><u><strong>Job Description:</strong></u></p><ol><li>Handle full sets of accounts for multiple clients, including data entry, reconciliations, and month-end/year-end closing.</li><li>Prepare unaudited financial statements in accordance with Singapore Financial Reporting Standards (SFRS).</li><li>Assist in the preparation and filing of GST and corporate tax returns.</li><li>Liaise directly with clients regarding accounting, financial, and tax-related queries.</li><li>Maintain accurate accounting records and ensure compliance with ACRA and IRAS requirements.</li><li>Perform ad-hoc accounting duties or administrative tasks as assigned.</li></ol><p><u><strong>Requirements: </strong></u></p><ul><li>Bookkeeper who can perform full set accounts. </li></ul><p><br />Tan Yen Zhen (Chen Yan Zhen) Reg No: R25138932</p><p>The SupremeHR Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</p>",
